Package game.items

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Consumable
    An interface which will be implemented by the item which is consumable by an actor.
    Purchasable
    The Purchasable interface represents items that can be purchased by an actor.
    Sellable
    The Sellable interface represents items that can be sold by an actor.
    Upgradable
    An interface for items that can be upgraded in the game.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BloodBerry
    The `BloodBerry` class represents an item in the game called BloodBerry.
    HealingVial
    The HealingVial class represents an item in the game that can be consumed by an actor to increase their health.
    Key
    A class that represents a Key that can unlock gates.
    RefreshingFlask
    A class that represents a Refreshing Flask item in the game.
    Runes
    A class that represents a stack of runes as an item in the game.
